                                    2004 - Prior                


RCS, Inc.


                  RCS, Inc., part of RCS MediaGroup SpA, is an American company located in White Plains, NY, that develops radio computing services. The firm was founded by Larry A. Webb.                




Chief Financial Officer & Vice President

