Christopher Smith
Executive Managing Director, Global Head of Strategy and Corporate Development
                                                                                    
                            Chris Smith is Head of BGC’s Strategic Investments Group, which focuses on driving revenues, margins and profits through acquisitions and strategic initiatives. In addition, Mr. Smith is responsible for coordinating the Company’s global brokerage rates and BGC’s businesses in South America and Turkey.                                                        
                        



Eric Hirschhorn
Chief Information Officer
                                                                                    
                            Eric Hirschhorn is responsible for product development and infrastructure management of BGC’s suite of electronic broking technology products and systems.                                                        
                        



Philip Cramp
Head of Credit, Repo and EGBs in London
                                                                                    
                            Philip Cramp joins BGC with 30 years of financial markets experience. He was previously Head of Credit EMEA at ICAP, a position he held from 2012 to June 2014. Prior to this, Mr. Cramp was Managing Director of Euro Interest Rate Swaps.                                                         
                        



Robert Miller
Senior Managing Director and Head of US Credit
                                                                                    
                            Robert Miller is a Senior Managing Director and Head of US Credit. With a career spanning more than 25 years, Robert joined BGC Partners in 2009 from Tullet Prebon PLC, having worked since then across the New York business.                                                        
                        



Len Harvey
Executive Managing Director and General Manager, Latin America
                                                                                    
                            Len Harvey is responsible for overseeing the brokerage businesses in the Latin American region.  He joined BGC Partners in 2008.                                                        
                        



 


